# Example projects: ignore root-level transient state. The matching
# entries inside `.samuel/` (lock, run/, plugins/, builtins/) live in
# each example's own `.samuel/.gitignore`, which samuel init writes
# for every new project — so we don't have to duplicate them here.
examples/*/CLAUDE.md
examples/*/samuel.lock
